full_text: “Egregious” might be a bit of a stretch https://t.co/KeXl6dUQvt
I'm still in disbelief we lost Jose Fernandez so young. It's ridiculous how dominant he was before age 25 - both before and after TJS.
The Pelicans got two defensive studs outside the first round in the same year. It’s unbelievable.
